**Visual patterns:** 8–15 nail close-up images typical across ranking posts; most use grid layouts without narrative.

**Recommended image count:** 10–12 images — each must show a distinct finish or design variation (velvet, chrome, matte, glossy, aura, floral, glitter, ombre, jelly). Do not use generic single-colour shots. Visual storytelling across the plum spectrum is the differentiator.

